entities.description: A score ranging from 0 to 24 indicating the level of psychological distress over the past 30 days.
A score ranging from 0 to 24 indicating the level of psychological distress during the worst month of the past year.
The higher K6 score between the past month K6 total score (KSSLR6MON) and the K6 total score in the worst month of the past year (KSSLR6YR), if the worst month was not the past 30 days.
Indicator of serious psychological distress in the past month based on K6 total score.
Indicator of serious psychological distress in the past year based on K6 total score.

relationships.description: Relates KSSLR6MON to its score range.
Defines the K6 total score in the past month.
Defines the K6 total score in the worst month of the past year.
Defines the higher K6 score between the past month and the worst month in the past year.
Relates the K6 past month total score to the serious psychological distress indicator in the past month.
Relates the higher K6 score to the serious psychological distress indicator in the past year.
